tweets.text:
NEW: Another illegal immigrant has been accused of murder in Virginia.

@DHSgov identified Anibal Armando Chavarria Muy, 38, who allegedly repeatedly stabbed a man to death in Fairfax County Sunday, as a "criminal illegal alien from Guatemala," @NickMinock reports.

It comes just a month after 41-year-old mother Stephanie Minter was allegedly fatally stabbed at a Fairfax Co. bus stop by Sierra Leone national Abdul Jalloh, 32, who had 30 prior arrests.

